    <div class="row p-0">
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 p-0">
            <img src="~/Content/livemusic.png" alt="Live Music" class="image-fit" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 padded-text off-white">
            <h2>We Have Live Music on Friday</h2>
            <p>What are your thoughts about live music? A great band play behind? An amazing vocalist? Or a song that you can sing along and enjoy it? We have all you need right here at the Cozy Coffee Bean. We invite you to come to chill with us at perfect Friday night live music from 8 PM. Also, we have both International artists and local artists so that our guests can choose their favourite taste of music. Also, we have requested song by our guests too! Contact us by email or phone number for reserved the table today.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row p-0">
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 padded-text">
            <h2>Comedy Night Sundays</h2>
            <p>Happiness is making someone laugh, and we want to make our guests feel joy and relaxed like a quick pause in this crowded Toronto city. We strongly believe that any comedians on stage will make you feel delighted with their jokes even laugh out loud! </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 p-0">
            <img src="~/Content/comedians.png" alt="Store front and employees" class="image-fit" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row p-0">
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 p-0">
            <img src="~/Content/resizedfriends.png" alt="Live Music" class="image-fit" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 padded-text off-white">
            <h2>Come In and See</h2>
            <p>What makes us more unique than other coffee shops is that we have live entertainment every month on specific days. We cover everything from live music to comedy which can please every guest that comes to Cozy Bean Coffee. Whether the hot or cold weather, the Cozy Bean Coffee is a safe place for every soul out there to go and enjoy the entertainment that we bring to you. The Cozy Bean Coffee is not a regular coffee shop, and it is a place to slow your pace down a bit in this busy big city.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
